<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="597" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,541,1287]" pageId="6" pageNumber="597">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1189,1215]" pageId="6" pageNumber="597">Remarks.</emphasis>
The specimens examined in this study have a longer wingspan (18.0–21.0 mm) than the wingspan of the 
<typeStatus box="[223,271,1226,1252]" pageId="6" pageNumber="597">type</typeStatus>
series (14.0–15.0 mm). This species is newly recorded in 
<collectingCountry box="[924,994,1225,1251]" name="China" pageId="6" pageNumber="597">China</collectingCountry>
, and its female is described for the first time.
</paragraph>
